We met some of the world’s best hackers in Las Vegas, who are breaking into systems (legally) and earning massive payouts for uncovering security vulnerabilities. From hacking cars to protecting major companies, these bug bounty hunters are reshaping the future of cybersecurity—and sometimes making millions in just a few days!
